item.title: It wont let me log on
item.dc:creator: @Steviie Steviie
item.description:
@Steviie wrote:

if you’re trying to get on someone elses server, DON’T click start new server or what ever.

Just simply type in their IP and Port number first.

If you cannot connect it’s the owner of the server has turned it off.

P.S this sometimes happens to me (when i know the server is online. i just close moparscape and re-open).
